# AI Prompt 管理器 - 项目架构图

## 1. 整体多端架构

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Clients[客户端层]
        Web[apps_web]
        Desktop[apps_desktop]
        Mobile[apps_mobile]
        Extension[apps_extension]
        Mini[apps_miniprogram]
    end

    subgraph Shared[共享层]
        Pkg[packages_shared]
    end

    subgraph Backend[后端层]
        Auth[Supabase_Auth]
        DB[(PostgreSQL)]
        Fn[Edge_Function]
    end

    Desktop --> Web
    Mobile --> Web
    Web --> Auth
    Web --> DB
    Web --> Fn
    Extension --> Auth
    Extension --> DB
    Extension --> Fn
    Mini --> Auth
    Mini --> DB
    Mini --> Fn
    Web -.-> Pkg
```

