## 2. Web 应用架构

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph WebApp[apps_web]
        App[App.tsx]
        Router[React_Router]
        subgraph Pages[页面]
            Login[LoginPage]
            Dashboard[DashboardPage]
            PromptList[PromptListPage]
            PromptDetail[PromptDetailPage]
            Settings[SettingsPage]
        end
        subgraph Contexts[状态管理]
            AuthCtx[AuthContext]
            PromptCtx[PromptContext]
        end
        Supabase[lib_supabase.ts]
    end

    App --> Router --> Pages
    Pages --> Contexts --> Supabase
```

