## 6. 跨端数据流

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    subgraph Web端[Web_Desktop_Mobile]
        WUI[React_Pages]
        WCtx[Context_状态]
        WAPI[supabase-js]
    end

    subgraph 扩展端[Extension]
        EUI[App.tsx]
        EHook[usePromptData]
        ELocal[chrome_storage]
        EAPI[supabase-js]
    end

    subgraph 小程序[Miniprogram]
        MUI[Page_页面]
        MLocal[wx_storage]
        MAPI[wx_request]
    end

    subgraph Cloud[Supabase]
