    EHook --> ELocal
    EHook --> EAPI
    MUI --> MLocal
    MUI --> MAPI

    WAPI --> Auth
    WAPI --> DB
    WAPI --> Fn
    EAPI --> Auth
    EAPI --> DB
    EAPI --> Fn
    MAPI --> Auth
    MAPI --> DB
    MAPI --> Fn
```

